{"tid":656984,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[UST]啲civil莊當Hall係soc房架屌你","createTime":"2018-05-07T16:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T07:18:53.000Z","uid":113953,"like":294,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"a4028e9d7c5a7cc1626c47287a57c6473966066f","tid":656984,"uid":113953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今日返到hall <br />\n見到到大大隻招牌棟係中間<br />\n門都開唔到咁濟<br />\n我即刻火都來黎埋<br />\n<br />\n上個星期五好聲好氣叫你執好張血色CIVIL枱<br />\n始終大家係roommate <br />\n我覺得可以用商討來解決<br />\n你應承話會搬走<br />\n好！我信你！<br />\n結果？<br />\n一張枱唔夠<br />\n就黎多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一架車</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一堂梯</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩塊牌</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三個波</span></span><br />\n成疊紙皮<br />\n原來成支莊應承你搬走的意思係指變本加厲咁放更多的嘢<br />\n原來一支莊係可以咁無口齒<br />\n<br />\n我明白你地支莊不嬲想我搬走<br />\n但我畢竟係全年hall <br />\n我都有畀hall fee 的<br />\n憑咩我間房就要被你支莊滾搞成咁樣<br />\n<br />\n你大大隻字放中間都係想promotion 啫<br />\n小弟今日我都只能幫你地支莊宣傳一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a71fea753cc33a7a0fa3cf9d47d2613bbee24d","tid":656984,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac2b5453825cee9104d11f2af5472ec98f1de41","tid":656984,"uid":34444,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"打柒佢啦呢啲仆街得寸進尺"},{"pid":"c713810dd692ec34c5211a8fd6fbdab53af38777","tid":656984,"uid":135293,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"Call舍監la"},{"pid":"8cf1b7f6a867f5ab0573d723cf37222f81cc99d6","tid":656984,"uid":134522,"like":8,"disli